show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/3mg5PS
show.description: A girl names Raksha arrives in the city from her village with her mother to stay with her sister Nisha, but Nisha refuses to acknowledge them due to social status. Hiding her true identity, Raksha reinvents herself as a wealthy heiress. An old pendant leads Rksha to Mrs. Patel, the mother she lost long ago. When an attack on her mother unfolds, secrets come to light—and a DNA test reveals the truth: Raksha is the real CEO. Nisha’s lies are exposed before the media, and Raksha regains her true identity, mother, and dignity.
